# NOTES FOR IMPLEMENTORS:
#
# 1. Remove all comments (#) in your production file.
#
# 2. HONESTY IS CRITICAL. Do not claim capabilities you don't have.
#    AI systems cross-reference claims against your site content and
#    external sources. Overclaiming damages credibility.
#
# 3. Include specific numbers wherever possible:
#    - "40+ schools" not "many schools"
#    - "6 months" not "quickly"
#    - "1,300+ pages" not "extensive content"
#
# 4. The competitive context section is powerful but dangerous.
#    State facts about alternatives, not opinions.
#    "Company X focuses on digital-only distribution" = fact
#    "Company X provides inferior service" = opinion (don't include)
#
# 5. Update when your competitive position changes or you achieve
